{"article_id":"PD0AerCVy9klkJOL","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"WASHINGTON -","depth":1},{"id":1,"text":"President Trump suggested Friday","depth":7},{"id":2,"text":"that Senate Republicans may not be able to push through their health care plan","depth":8},{"id":3,"text":"meant to repeal and replace Obamacare","depth":8},{"id":4,"text":"and suggested a conservative-endorsed alternative instead .","depth":6},{"id":5,"text":"The president tweeted ,","depth":8},{"id":6,"text":"`` If Republican Senators are unable to pass what they are working on now ,","depth":9},{"id":7,"text":"they should immediately REPEAL ,","depth":10},{"id":8,"text":"and then REPLACE at a later date ! ''","depth":10},{"id":9,"text":"If Republican Senators are unable to pass what they are working on now ,","depth":8},{"id":10,"text":"they should immediately REPEAL ,","depth":9},{"id":11,"text":"and then REPLACE at a later date !","depth":9},{"id":12,"text":"- Donald J. Trump","depth":8},{"id":13,"text":"( @ realDonaldTrump )","depth":8},{"id":14,"text":"June 30 , 2017","depth":7},{"id":15,"text":"It 's the second time this week","depth":9},{"id":16,"text":"that Trump seemed to recognize how difficult it may be to get this bill through the Senate .","depth":9},{"id":17,"text":"On Monday , he said on Twitter ,","depth":9},{"id":18,"text":"`` Republican Senators are working very hard","depth":13},{"id":19,"text":"to get there ,","depth":13},{"id":20,"text":"with no help from the Democrats .","depth":12},{"id":21,"text":"Not easy !","depth":11},{"id":22,"text":"Perhaps just let OCare crash & burn ! ''","depth":10},{"id":23,"text":"A day later ,","depth":9},{"id":24,"text":"as Republican opposition to the legislation grew ,","depth":9},{"id":25,"text":"Senate Majority Leader Mitch McConnell of Kentucky announced","depth":10},{"id":26,"text":"that he would postpone a vote on the legislation until after the July Fourth recess .","depth":10},{"id":27,"text":"McConnell needs at minimum 50 of the 52 Republicans in the Senate","depth":11},{"id":28,"text":"to vote for the bill .","depth":11},{"id":29,"text":"Currently , there are at least eight senators outright opposed to the legislation","depth":11},{"id":30,"text":"and a handful of others","depth":12},{"id":31,"text":"who have expressed concern .","depth":12},{"id":32,"text":"Still , White House deputy press secretary Sarah Huckabee Sanders said","depth":10},{"id":33,"text":"the tweet did not represent a change in Trump ' s position .","depth":10},{"id":34,"text":"\" We 're still fully committed to pushing through with the Senate at this point ,","depth":11},{"id":35,"text":"but we ' re looking at every possible option","depth":12},{"id":36,"text":"for repealing and replacing Obamacare , \"","depth":12},{"id":37,"text":"she said .","depth":10},{"id":38,"text":"Sen. Ben Sasse , R-Neb .","depth":13},{"id":39,"text":"- a frequent Trump critic and someone","depth":14},{"id":40,"text":"who has stayed relatively quiet on the health care debate so far -","depth":14},{"id":41,"text":"said Friday on Fox News","depth":12},{"id":42,"text":"that he agreed with the president on repealing now and replacing later .","depth":11},{"id":43,"text":"`` If we do n't get this resolved by the Monday of the next week , July 10 ,","depth":13},{"id":44,"text":"if there is n't a combined repeal and replace plan ,","depth":13},{"id":45,"text":"I 'm writing a letter to the president this morning","depth":13},{"id":46,"text":"urging him to call on us to separate them , ''","depth":13},{"id":47,"text":"Sasse said .","depth":11},{"id":48,"text":"Sasse said","depth":11},{"id":49,"text":"the Senate should repeal the health care law","depth":12},{"id":50,"text":"and then Trump should require senators to stick around during their August recess","depth":13},{"id":51,"text":"to craft a replacement .","depth":13},{"id":52,"text":"He also recommended","depth":11},{"id":53,"text":"that the repeal be delayed for a year ,","depth":12},{"id":54,"text":"so lawmakers would have time","depth":13},{"id":55,"text":"to craft and put a repeal in place .","depth":13},{"id":56,"text":"Sasse pointed out","depth":9},{"id":57,"text":"that Republican lawmakers voted overwhelmingly in the past to repeal Obamacare","depth":10},{"id":58,"text":"without a replacement .","depth":10},{"id":59,"text":"However , those votes were largely symbolic","depth":9},{"id":60,"text":"because President Obama made clear","depth":10},{"id":61,"text":"he 'd always veto any attempts","depth":11},{"id":62,"text":"to undo his signature health care law .","depth":11},{"id":63,"text":"Sen. Rand Paul of Kentucky , one of the Republican senators","depth":10},{"id":64,"text":"who has said","depth":11},{"id":65,"text":"he can not vote for the proposed legislation","depth":12},{"id":66,"text":"as it stands ,","depth":12},{"id":67,"text":"agreed with the president 's Friday tweet ,","depth":9},{"id":68,"text":"saying","depth":9},{"id":69,"text":"that Obamacare should be repealed immediately .","depth":9},{"id":70,"text":"`` I have spoken to @ realDonaldTrump & Senate leadership about this","depth":10},{"id":71,"text":"and agree , ''","depth":10},{"id":72,"text":"he said on Twitter .","depth":9},{"id":73,"text":"`` Let 's keep our word","depth":13},{"id":74,"text":"to repeal","depth":13},{"id":75,"text":"then work on replacing right away . '' I have spoken to @ realDonaldTrump & Senate leadership about this","depth":12},{"id":76,"text":"and agree .","depth":11},{"id":77,"text":"Let 's keep our word to repeal","depth":11},{"id":78,"text":"then work on replacing right away .","depth":11},{"id":79,"text":"- Senator Rand Paul","depth":11},{"id":80,"text":"( @ RandPaul )","depth":11},{"id":81,"text":"June 30 , 2017","depth":10},{"id":82,"text":"But that message stands in contrast to a January conversation","depth":11},{"id":83,"text":"that Paul touted ,","depth":11},{"id":84,"text":"during which the then-president-elect agreed with him on repealing and replacing the same day .","depth":11},{"id":85,"text":"It was not immediately clear","depth":12},{"id":86,"text":"if the plan was to do so in two separate but simultaneous bills or one .","depth":12},{"id":87,"text":"I just spoke to @ realDonaldTrump","depth":11},{"id":88,"text":"and he fully supports my plan","depth":12},{"id":89,"text":"to replace Obamacare the same day","depth":13},{"id":90,"text":"we repeal it .","depth":13},{"id":91,"text":"The time","depth":12},{"id":92,"text":"to act","depth":12},{"id":93,"text":"is now .","depth":11},{"id":94,"text":"- Senator Rand Paul","depth":9},{"id":95,"text":"( @ RandPaul )","depth":9},{"id":96,"text":"January 7 , 2017","depth":7},{"id":97,"text":"Conservative interest groups expressed hope in a call with reporters Friday morning about the chances","depth":6},{"id":98,"text":"of a full repeal","depth":7},{"id":99,"text":"taking place first .","depth":7},{"id":100,"text":"`` It ' s good to see the president joining us in terms of the full repeal effort , ''","depth":7},{"id":101,"text":"said Ken Cuccinelli , president of the Senate Conservatives Fund PAC and former attorney general of Virginia .","depth":7},{"id":102,"text":"Cuccinelli has been a strong opponent of Obamacare","depth":8},{"id":103,"text":"and has sued over the health care law .","depth":8},{"id":104,"text":"`` It 's distressing to see so many Republicans","depth":9},{"id":105,"text":"who have lied about their commitment to repeal , ''","depth":9},{"id":106,"text":"he said .","depth":8},{"id":107,"text":"A senior GOP aide told","depth":7},{"id":108,"text":"that there are no plans underway","depth":8},{"id":109,"text":"to send a separate repeal bill to the Congressional Budget Office for analysis .","depth":8},{"id":110,"text":"The aide pointed out","depth":8},{"id":111,"text":"that the original plan had always been to repeal and replace separately ,","depth":9},{"id":112,"text":"but Trump and House Speaker Paul Ryan , R-Wis. , said","depth":10},{"id":113,"text":"that it was important to do the two simultaneously .","depth":10},{"id":114,"text":"That led to lawmakers changing course","depth":8},{"id":115,"text":"and focusing on a single bill .","depth":8},{"id":116,"text":"David Bozell , president of the conservative advocacy group ForAmerica , dismissed information","depth":8},{"id":117,"text":"coming from leadership aides in the Senate .","depth":8},{"id":118,"text":"`` President and Sen. Sasse kind of have their finger on the pulse a lot more","depth":9},{"id":119,"text":"than Senate leadership and their staff do , ''","depth":9},{"id":120,"text":"he told reporters .","depth":8},{"id":121,"text":"Nathan Nascimento , vice president of policy of the Koch funding arm Freedom Partners , said","depth":7},{"id":122,"text":"the two-step approach `` would put Congress and the administration in the position","depth":8},{"id":123,"text":"to keep their promise '' on health care .","depth":8},{"id":124,"text":"Trump 's health care tweet","depth":4},{"id":125,"text":"- along with another about crime and killings in Chicago -","depth":4},{"id":126,"text":"came as the hosts of Morning Joe , Mika Brzezinski and Joe Scarborough , addressed his Thursday Twitter attacks .","depth":3}],"relations":[{"parent":253,"left":0,"right":252,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":252,"left":249,"right":251,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":249,"left":222,"right":248,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":222,"left":140,"right":221,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":140,"left":130,"right":139,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":130,"left":129,"right":4,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":129,"left":1,"right":128,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":128,"left":2,"right":3,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":139,"left":136,"right":138,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":136,"left":133,"right":135,"relation":"restatement","nu